  wrong line type**   of pavement         dashed, edge of pavement = solid.

  **Not accounting    Profile vertical    NEVER scale vertical distances off
  for scale           scale ≠ horizontal  a profile using horizontal scale.
  distortion in       scale               Use labeled elevations only.
  profiles**                              

  **Forgetting pipe   Forgetting to add   Add OD (in ft) to invert to get
  size in cover       OD to invert        top of pipe before calculating
  calculations**      elevation           cover.

  **Double-counting   Shapes overlap when Sketch each sub-area and number
