  --------------------------------------------------------------------------

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **★ PRO TIP:** The GOLDEN RULE of measuring: always check your result
  against reality. If you get 500 linear feet of sewer pipe for a 50-foot
  wide lot, something is wrong. Develop a sense for typical quantities
  and flag results that seem unreasonable.

